</a>
</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><h4 class="field-content"><a href="https://www.worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/culture/interactive-storytelling-three-recent-video-games-serena-middleton">Interactive Storytelling in Three Recent Video Games
</a>
</h4></div><div><div class="blog-summary">As technology develops. it causes changes in the mediums that house our literature, but our human ability to tell stories stays the same. In addition…
